org.dgfoundation.amp.ar

Class Exporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dgfoundation.amp.ar.Exporter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PDFExporter, XLSExporter

    public abstract class Exporter
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class subclassed by any Exporter that provides alternate output schemas (PDF,XLS,CSV...) for Viewable entities. Exporters are java based viewers for Viewable items. They behave in the same way as jsp includes for html. Thus, an exporter for an object that has childen (like Reports or Columns) will always call any child exporters before exiting.
    Since:
    Aug 28, 2006
